    "\n",
    "This confirms that the dataset is **extremely imbalanced**, with fraud making up less than 1% of all transactions.\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "### Why this matters for Feature Engineering\n",
    "\n",
    "Even after creating new features, the model will still face the same challenge:\n",
    "\n",
    "- it sees far more legitimate transactions than fraudulent ones  \n",
